# ‚úÖ Recommended Way (Axios v1+): `AbortController`

Axios now supports the **native browser `AbortController`**, same as `fetch`.

***

## ‚úÖ Basic Axios Cancel Example

```js
import axios from "axios";

const controller = new AbortController();

axios.get("/api/data", {
  signal: controller.signal
})
.then(response => {
  console.log(response.data);
})
.catch(error => {
  if (error.name === "CanceledError") {
    console.log("Request cancelled");
  }
});
  
// ‚úÖ cancel request
controller.abort();
```

