# ‚úÖ Cancel Axios on Button Click

```js
let controller;

function fetchData() {
  if (controller) {
    controller.abort(); // cancel previous
  }

  controller = new AbortController();

  axios.get("/api/data", {
    signal: controller.signal
  });
}
```

‚úÖ Useful outside React lifecycle.

