# ‚úÖ Prevent State Update (Fallback Only)

If cancellation is not supported (old environments):

```js
useEffect(() => {
  let mounted = true;

  axios.get("/api/data").then(res => {
    if (mounted) setData(res.data);
  });

  return () => {
    mounted = false;
  };
}, []);
```

‚ö†ÔłŹ Request still runs  
‚úÖ Prevents stale state updates  
‚ĚĆ Not true cancellation

